    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "oh okay, i think i understand. well, the only reason i had that method was because i didn&#39;t know where that &quot;magic one liner&quot; was. hence, that&#39;s why i asked this stackoverflow question in the first place. if i already knew that one line <code>Arrays.asList(s)</code>, then why would i ask my question here on stackoverflow? i was surprised to find that this convenience method is in Arrays and not Collections."
