      "body" : "This is not working if given element implements Iterable&lt;T&gt;, for example: <code>Lists.newArrayList(Paths.get(&quot;&#47;usr&#47;local&#47;this&#47;is&#47;not&#47;single&#47;&zwnj;&#8203;element&quot;))</code>; what you want is create array with single path element, however, what you get is a list contains 7 path element."
