    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>With Java 8 Streams:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Stream.of(object).collect(Collectors.toList())\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or if you need a set:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Stream.of(object).collect(Collectors.toSet())\n</code></pre>\n"
