    "answer_id" : 40133991,
    "question_id" : 20358883,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Seeing as Guava gets a mention, I thought I would also suggest <a href=\"https://www.eclipse.org/collections/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Eclipse Collections</a> (formerly known as GS Collections).</p>\n\n<p>The following examples all return a <code>List</code> with a single item.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Lists.mutable.of(\"Just one item\");\nLists.mutable.with(\"Or use with\");\nLists.immutable.of(\"Maybe it must be immutable?\");\nLists.immutable.with(\"And use with if you want\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>There are similar methods for other collections.</p>\n"
  } ],
